# Storefront URL — “View store” / links (match your Vite dev port, often 8080 or 5173)
VITE_STORE_URL=http://localhost:8080

# Leave VITE_API_URL unset so the admin calls same-origin `/api/*`.
# Vite proxies `/api` to Express at http://127.0.0.1:5000 (see vite.config.ts).
# Alternative: set VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000 to talk to the API directly (backend must allow CORS from http://localhost:5174).
